g-guidance-al-hidayah","tag-jews-yahud","tag-manners-adab","tag-mercy-al-rahmah","tag-sneezing","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9yh","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":22340,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/03\/27\/seventy-three-sects\/","url_meta":{"origin":36721,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sects: Muslims will split into seventy-three sects","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 27, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Jews were divided into seventy-one or seventy-two sects, and the Christians were divided as well. My nation will divide into seventy three-sects.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2640 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41978,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/05\/31\/sneezing-praise-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36721,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sneezing: Praise Allah in all situations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you sneezes, let him say: All praise is due to Allah in every circumstance. Let those respond to him by saying: May Allah have mercy upon you. Let him respond to them by\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0