 \u201cIt is reported from Ibn Abbas that he said to fast on the ninth and tenth of the month and to do so\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/08\/prophet-rebukes-hafsa-safiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36721,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Pride: The Prophet rebukes Hafsa for insulting Safiyyah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: Safiyyah heard that Hafsa called her \u201cthe daughter of a Jew,\u201d so Safiyyah started crying. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered while she was crying and he said, \u201cWhat makes you cry?\u201d Safiyyah said, \u201cHafsa called me the daughter of a Jew.\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1975,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/18\/prophet-face-not-a-liar\/","url_meta":{"origin":36721,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: I knew his was not the face of a liar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Salaam reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to Medina, the people rushed toward him and it was said, \u201cThe Messenger of Allah has come!\u201d I came along with the people to see him and when I looked at the face of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0